statements.sql: select * from `users` where `id` = '4ec9f499-180c-4e81-9ba1-e79ebf36db8b' and `users`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `users` where (`user_type` = 'customer') and `users`.`deleted_at` is null
select count(*) as aggregate from `providers` where (`is_approved` = 1)

select IFNULL(sum(credit),0) as sums, YEAR(created_at) year, MONTH(created_at) month from `transactions` where `credit` > 0 and `to_user_account` in ('received_balance', 'total_withdrawn') and year(`created_at`) = '2023' group by `year`, `month`

select IFNULL(sum(credit),0) as sums, YEAR(created_at) year, MONTH(created_at) month from `transactions` where (`trx_type` = 'received_commission') and `to_user_account` in ('received_balance') or (`from_user_account` in ('received_balance')) and year(`created_at`) = '2023' group by `year`, `month`
select * from `transactions` where month(`created_at`) = '10' order by `created_at` desc limit 5
select * from `bookings` where `booking_status` = 'pending' order by `created_at` desc limit 5
select `providers`.*, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `providers`.`id` = `reviews`.`provider_id`) as `reviews_count` from `providers` where `is_approved` = 1 order by `avg_rating` desc limit 5

select * from `users` where `user_type` = 'provider-admin' and `users`.`id` in ('ahmad.bedeirk4@gmail.com', 'hazem@zahra-kw.com', 'info@fdlights.com', 'ryan@askafi.com', 'testm1@repair.com') and `users`.`deleted_at` is null

select `zone_id`, count(*) as total from `bookings` where exists (select * from `zones` where `bookings`.`zone_id` = `zones`.`id` and `is_active` = 1) and month(`created_at`) = '10' group by `zone_id`
